lass=\"token punctuation\">-</span> npm run test<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>watch</code></pre></div>\n<p>лСР л≤ИмІЄ м∞љмЭА лєИ paneк≥Љ нЕМмК§нКЄ watch л™®лУЬлВШ мДЬл≤ДмЩА к∞ЩмЭі foreground мГБм£ЉнХШлКФ л™Ел†ємЦіл•Љ мЛ§нЦЙнХі лСРлКФ м∞љмЭД лґДнХ†нХі лСФлЛ§.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ajeetdsouza/zoxide\">zoxide</a>л•Љ мВђмЪ©нХШлѓАл°Ь,\nнД∞лѓЄлДРмЭД мЧік≥† <code class=\"language-text\">z my</code> мЮЕл†• нЫД <code class=\"language-text\">tmuxn</code>лІМ мЮЕл†•нХШл©і к∞Ьл∞Ь нЩШк≤љмЭі м§АлєДк∞А лБЭлВЬлЛ§.</p>\n<h2 id=\"нФМлЯђкЈЄмЭЄ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"нФМлЯђкЈЄмЭЄ permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>нФМлЯђкЈЄмЭЄ</h2>\n<p>Tmux нФМлЯђкЈЄмЭЄк≥Љ нФМлЯђкЈЄмЭЄмЭД кіАл¶ђнХШлКФ лІ§лЛИм†Ак∞А мЮИлЛ§.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/tmux-plugins/tpm\">TPM</a>мЭА Tmux Plugin ManagerлЛ§.\nмВђмЪ©нХШкЄ∞ мЬДнХімДЬ нФДл°Ьм†ЭнКЄл•Љ Clone л∞Ык≥†, <code class=\"language-text\">.tmux.conf</code>мЧР мД§м†ХмЭД мґФк∞АнХімХЉ нХШлКФ к≥Љм†ХмЭі л≤Ик±∞л°≠лЛ§.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/tmux-plugins/tmux-resurrect\">Tmux Resurrect</a>лКФ мДЄмЕШмЭД м†АмЮ•нХШк≥† л≥µмЫРнХШлКФ нФМлЯђкЈЄмЭЄмЭД мВђмЪ©нЦИмЧИлКФлН∞,\nнКєл≥ДнЮИ мВђмЪ©нХ† мЭЉмЭі мЧЖмЦімДЬ м†Ьк±∞нЦИлЛ§.</p>\n<h2 id=\"oh-my-zshмЭШ-tmux-нФМлЯђкЈЄмЭЄ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#oh-my-zsh%EC%9D%98-tmux-%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"oh my zshмЭШ tmux нФМлЯђкЈЄмЭЄ permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Oh My ZshмЭШ Tmux нФМлЯђкЈЄмЭЄ</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/tree/master/plugins/tmux\">Oh My ZshмЭШ Tmux нФМлЯђкЈЄмЭЄ</a>мЭД мВђмЪ©нХШл©і нОЄл¶ђ кЄ∞лК•мЭД м†Ьк≥µнХЬлЛ§.\nкЄ∞м°і <code class=\"language-text\">tmux</code> л™Ел†ємЦіл•Љ wrapping нХШлКФлН∞, <code class=\"language-text\">tmux</code>лІМ мЮЕл†•нХШл©і мДЄмЕШмЭі мЧЖмЬЉл©і мГЭмД±нХШк≥†, мЮИмЬЉл©і attach нХЬлЛ§.\nкЈЄ мЩЄмЧРлПД л™З к∞АмІА aliasмЩА мЮРлПЩ к∞±мЛ† кЄ∞лК•мЭД м†Ьк≥µнХЬлЛ§лКФлН∞ к∞ЬмЭЄм†БмЬЉл°ЬлКФ нХДмЪФнХШмІА мХКлЛ§.</p>\n<p>нФМлЯђкЈЄмЭЄ мД§м†ХмЭА <code class=\"language-text\">~/.zshrc</code>мЧР мґФк∞АнХЬлЛ§.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  tmux\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>zsh нФМлЯђкЈЄмЭЄмЧРмДЬлКФ <a href=\"https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/blob/881c8b78d3e3ade9bccfddb3e616842807d07a59/plugins/tmux/tmux.plugin.zsh#L110-L161\">мЭі кЄ∞лК•мЭШ кµђнШД</a>мЭі м°∞кЄИ л≥µмЮ°нХЬлН∞, нФМлЯђкЈЄмЭЄ мЧЖмЭі мХљмЛЭмЬЉл°Ь кµђнШДнХ† мИШ мЮИлЛ§.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">command</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-v</span> tmux <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;></span> /dev/null<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">then</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function-name function\">_tmux_run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-n</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$@</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">then</span>\n      <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">command</span> tmux <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$@</span>\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span>\n      tmux attach\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">fi</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  compdef _tmux _tmux_run\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">alias</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">tmux</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>_tmux_run\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fi</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>мГИл°ЬмЪі мДЄмЕШмЭД мГЭмД±нХШлКФ лґАлґДмЭА мГЭлЮµнЦИмІАлІМ, мШµмЕШмЭі мЮИмЬЉл©і <code class=\"language-text\">tmux $@</code>л•Љ мЛ§нЦЙнХШк≥†, мШµмЕШмЭі мЧЖмЬЉл©і <code class=\"language-text\">tmux attach</code>л•Љ мЛ§нЦЙнХЬлЛ§.\n<code class=\"language-text\">compdef</code>лКФ <code class=\"language-text\">tmux</code> л™Ел†ємЦімЭШ мЮРлПЩ мЩДмД±мЭД м†Ьк≥µнХЬлЛ§.</p>\n<h2 id=\"iterm2-tmux-нЖµнХ©\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#iterm2-tmux-%ED%86%B5%ED%95%A9\" aria-label=\"iterm2 tmux нЖµнХ© permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4